### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ لَهُمْ عَذَابٌ شَدِيدٌ ۖ وَٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ وَعَمِلُوا۟ ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ لَهُم مَّغْفِرَةٌ وَأَجْرٌ كَبِيرٌ</span>

### English

Those who disbelieve will have a severe punishment. But those who believe and do good will have forgiveness and a great reward.